text: Kawawa High School Kanagawa Prefectural Kawawa High School (神奈川県立川和高等学校, Kanagawa Kenritsu Kawawa Kōtōgakkō) is a high school in Tsuzuki-ku, Yokohama, Japan, founded in 1962. The school is operated by the Kanagawa Prefectural Board of Education. == References == ==Notable students and teachers== *Hideki Arai * ==External links== * School Website Category:High schools in Yokohama Category:Educational institutions established in 1962 Category:1962 establishments in Japan
